<div class="col-md-12" style="height: 75px"></div>
<div class="col-md-3"></div>
<div class="col-md-6">
  <div class="col-md-12 fish-user-info">
    <h1 class="fish-h1"><%= @user.login %> profile</h1>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="fish-profile-photo">
        <%= image_tag 'example_profile.jpg' %> 
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet enim. Etiam ullamcorper. Suspendisse a pellentesque dui, non felis. Maecenas malesuada elit lectus felis, malesuada ultricies. Curabitur et ligula. Ut molestie a, ultricies porta urna. Vestibulum commodo volutpat a, convallis ac, laoreet enim. Phasellus fermentum in, dolor.      
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-12" style="height: 25px"></div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2 class="fish-h2">Change password</h2>
    <%= form_for :user, url: user_set_password_path(@user) do |f| %>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.password_field :password_old, :placeholder => 'old password' %>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.password_field :password, :placeholder => 'new password' %>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :placeholder => 'confirm new password' %>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.submit "Change password", :class => 'button-link' %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h1 class="fish-h1">
      <%= link_to 'My wordlists', wordlists_url %>
    </h1>
    <h1 class="fish-h1">
      <%= link_to 'My exams', exams_url %>
    </h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-3"></div>
